Developer Terms of Use
des:
See an eye doctor via a video visit in less than an hour. Our national network of telehealth eye doctors can provide care for non-emergency eye conditions such as:

Renewal of prescriptions for eyeglasses
Pink / Red Eye
Dry Eye 
Concerns related to contact lenses
Eye wellness
Styes 
Medical prescriptions 
Test your vision
and more

Request an appointment by "Alexa, make an appointment with eye doctor" or "Alexa, call eyecarelive" or "Alexa, call eye doctor to renew my prescription", "Alexa, I would like to test my vision", "Alexa, test my vision"

EyecareLive will request to provide the following information to schedule an appointment with an eye doctor licensed in your state:

Name of the patient
Zip code of the patient
Mobile phone number for doctor to call

Once an appointment has been requested, you will receive a text message with instructions to prepare for the video call with an eye doctor. You can let the doctor know if you would prefer only an audio call instead. 

Credit card is charged only after you have seen a doctor. You may see a hold placed on your card for $59 prior to the appointment. Credit card is not charged if appointment is canceled.

For support inquiries, please contact support@eyecarelive.com
